# CTO Map — Cline/Roo Rules

## Project
52-week Technical CTO curriculum tracker. Next.js 14 App Router, TypeScript, Prisma/SQLite, Tailwind CSS.

## Must Do
- Add dark: variants to ALL Tailwind classes (text, bg, border, placeholder)
- min-h-[44px] min-w-[44px] on buttons, links, checkboxes
- 'use client'; on components with hooks/state/events
- Use useToast() for notifications, useProgress() for global state
- After task completion changes: calculateDayCompletion() → update Day → check Week
- npm install --legacy-peer-deps

## Must Not
- Don't use Pages Router (no getServerSideProps)
- Don't use any type — use interfaces from lib/types.ts
- Don't put callback props in useEffect deps (use useRef)
- Don't import prisma in client components
- Don't use external UI libraries (Tailwind only)

## Key Files
- prisma/schema.prisma — database schema
- lib/types.ts — all TypeScript interfaces
- lib/progress-context.tsx — global progress state
- lib/completion-calculator.ts — day completion logic
- app/Providers.tsx — context providers wrapper

## API Note
GET /api/task-items?dayId=X returns { learn: TaskItem[], build: TaskItem[] } not a flat array.
